name: Canadian North Retiring 737-200s
description:
Last week, Canadian North announced in an article published by Nunatsiaq News that they would unfortunately be retiring their Boeing 737-200s.

These are the last 737-200s to be based in Western Canada, and are the only ones I've had the privilege of flying on. They'll be missed!
